{"tid":2445141,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)冬蔭功 拳霸 女拳霸 懲罰者1-2","createTime":"2021-03-13T11:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T17:41:44.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ecf3c642ebdcc50085fa7b077716699633852cb","tid":2445141,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">支肺已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=e004cee5\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=763b837c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=1b0098e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://bestmartialartsmovies.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/tony-jaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbestmartialartsmovies.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F12%2Ftony-jaa.jpg&h=95515d61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a7/HKFilm_JiJaYanin1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa7%2FHKFilm_JiJaYanin1.jpg&h=b40ec73d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cf/Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg/220px-Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fcf%2FPunisherwarzoneteaser.jpg%2F220px-Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg&h=08597fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事講述在一個泰國寧靜的村落裏，純樸善良的阿錦（東尼嘉）與父親相依為命，他們過著簡單而開心的生活。當年曾擔任泰王御兵的父親閒時還會教授御兵所操練的拳術予阿錦，希望他日練成後可以為國王效力。<br />\n此外，兩父子並計劃將家中飼養的大象呈獻給國王。在潑水節前夕，父親雀躍地跟村長商量如何將心愛的象呈獻給國皇，豈料村長另有圖謀，與壞人互相勾結，藉口把大象送往身體檢查，把大象運往澳洲作黑市交易..<br />\n<br />\n2.朗．柏都（Nong Pra-Du）為泰國一寧靜小村莊，村民信奉佛教，尤其是寺內的安北佛（Ong Bak）。可惜，無良村民阿堂砍掉安北佛的頭，賣予不法商人謀取暴利，全村頓時恐懼不安。看守佛寺的阿丁，決定單人匹馬前赴曼谷，誓要將佛頭奪回&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.自閉症少女雪（Sen，琴嘉飾）自小與母親珊本（Sin）相依為命。珊本為泰國黑幫頭目八哥的手下，因與日本黑幫頭目岸本（Masashi，阿部寬飾）相戀，兩人被泰國黑道中人視為眼中釘，誓要除之而後快。岸本為保性命，不得已玩美女人日本。珊本母女四處逃避，卻依然難逃黑幫魔掌.....<br />\n<br />\n4.弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特（托馬斯&middot;簡Thomas Jane 飾）的生命中，絕大部分時間都在於死神賽跑。早年在海軍陸戰隊服役，退役後又進入FBI。在槍砲火光中生活了多年之後，弗蘭克不願再整日收到死亡的威脅，家人整日為他擔驚受怕。所以，他決定提前退休與妻兒享受平靜的生活。可是，在最後的一次任務中，卻因意外使一名無辜青年死亡..<br />\n<br />\n5.本想歸隱田園，與家人共度天倫的FBI探員弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特，無奈的在黑幫殺掉妻<br />\n兒之後走向了黑暗復仇的不歸路。弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特大難不死，在悲痛過後開始成為這個城市裡隱秘的&ldquo;懲罰者&rdquo;，在黑暗中打擊那些猖狂的犯罪分子的頭號先鋒。.....<br />\n<br />\n7 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=05d583e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=b3ecf954\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3abe690e3263404c068bffdb30030b3b7676cf","tid":2445141,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0136ed57c779968b88ab49800eb186d68600a3","tid":2445141,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad215b8ceaf4b94189746966f80b8d84b60eca92","tid":2445141,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a670fce7c0beca9148fee6545b7a61392088e412","tid":2445141,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T16:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3309472fb206bc22b94e9f6cf9d8f8d9fc951a42","tid":2445141,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"想試下同女拳霸隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2bb319cc9abfd28fc49ac5